title: Chuncheon FC
text: Chuncheon Citizen FC () is a South Korean <a href="association%20football">football</a> club based in <a href="Chuncheon">Chuncheon</a>, <a href="Gangwon-do%20%28South%20Korea%29">Gangwon</a>. The club plays in the <a href="K3%20League">K3 League</a>, the third tier of South Korean football. Chuncheon FC's home stadium is <a href="Chuncheon%20Stadium">Chuncheon Stadium</a>.
